{"word":"H1069 - בָּכַר - bâkar - baw-kar' - Make firstborn - முதற்பேறானவனாக்கு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּכַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâkar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-kar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Make firstborn / முதற்பேறானவனாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முதற்பேறானவனாயிரு, புதுக்கனிகளைகொடு, தலையீற்றானவனாயிரு,"},{"paragraph":"முதல் விசை பிள்ளை பெறு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be born first"},{"paragraph":"a) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to bear early, new fruit"},{"paragraph":"2) to give the right of the firstborn"},{"paragraph":"a) to make as firstborn"},{"paragraph":"b) to constitute as firstborn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be born a firstling"},{"paragraph":"2) to be made a firstling"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) one bearing her first child"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>burst</i> the womb, that is, (causatively) <i>bear</i> or <i>make early fruit</i> (of woman or tree); also (as denominatively from <a href=\"#/H1061 - בִּכּוּר - bikkûwr - bik-koor'/1061\">H1061</a>) to <i>give the birthright: - </i>make firstborn, be firstling, bring forth first child (new fruit)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1060 - בְּכֹור - bᵉkôwr - bek-ore'/1060\">H1060</a>, <a href=\"#/H1061 - בִּכּוּר - bikkûwr - bik-koor'/1061\">H1061</a>, <a href=\"#/H1062 - בְּכֹורָה - bᵉkôwrâh - bek-o-raw'/1062\">H1062</a>, <a href=\"#/H1063 - בִּכּוּרָה - bikkûwrâh - bik-koo-raw'/1063\">H1063</a>, <a href=\"#/H1064 - בְּכֹורַת - Bᵉkôwrath - bek-o-rath'/1064\">H1064</a>, <a href=\"#/H1067 - בְּכִירָה - bᵉkîyrâh - bek-ee-raw'/1067\">H1067</a>, <a href=\"#/H1069 - בָּכַר - bâkar - baw-kar'/1069\">H1069</a>, <a href=\"#/H1070 - בֶּכֶר - beker - beh'-ker/1070\">H1070</a>, <a href=\"#/H1071 - בֶכֶר - Beker - beh'-ker/1071\">H1071</a>, <a href=\"#/H1072 - בִּכְרָה - bikrâh - bik-raw'/1072\">H1072</a>, <a href=\"#/H1073 - בַּכֻּרָה - bakkurâh - bak-koo-raw'/1073\">H1073</a>, <a href=\"#/H1074 - בֹּכְרוּ - Bôkᵉrûw - bo-ker-oo'/1074\">H1074</a>, <a href=\"#/H1075 - בִּכְרִי - Bikrîy - bik-ree'/1075\">H1075</a>, <a href=\"#/H1076 - בַּכְרִי - Bakrîy - bak-ree'/1076\">H1076</a>, <a href=\"#/H1081 - בַּלְאֲדָן - Balʼădân - bal-ad-awn'/1081\">H1081</a>"}]}